    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-06-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-06-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="407"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d407">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.796/6–2544</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">New Zealand Legation</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Aide-Mémoire</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The New Zealand Legation is in receipt of <hi rend="italic">Aide-Mémoire</hi>
                    from the Department of State dated June 24, 1944,<note n="43" xml:id="d407fn43"
                        >See footnote 35, <ref target="#pg_494">p. 494</ref>.</note> in reference to
                    the development of international air transportation.</p>
                <p>The Prime Minister of New Zealand will be in Washington from July 4 to July 9,
                    inclusive, and will be pleased to begin exploratory conversations in Washington
                    and to meet representatives of the United States Government at a mutually
                    convenient time between the dates mentioned.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-06-25">June 25,
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
